Header.Title: Merrni zgjidhjet tatimore që meritoni
Hader.Content: Një software i fuqishëm që automatizon nga fillimi në fund ciklin tatimor dhe ju ndihmon në ofrimin e rezultateve më te mira financiare për klientët tuaj. Arrini performancë të jashtëzakonshme duke përdorur vetëm nje platform.
Header.p.Trail: 14 ditë provë falas. Nuk nevoitet kartel bankare.
FeaturesCard.Title: Eksploro veqoritë
FeaturesCard.Description: Software tatimor i njohur per thjeshtësine e përdorimit dhe rritjen e produktivitetit, si kurrë më parë ofrimin e shërbimeve profesionale tek klientët tuaj.
FeaturesCard.Description1: Complete your provision with power and precision using unprecedented automation in a single system
FeaturesCard.Description2: Your entire spectrum of compliance work, from estimates, extensions, returns, and new IRS filings, to RAR integrated in a single, secure system.
FeaturesCard.Description3: Gain control, speed, and efficiency, also instant access to data for analytics and planning.
FeaturesCard.Description4: IncorporateTax automation gives you better ways to get, manage and use data.
FeaturesCard.Description5: Get immediate value from core product automation and explore complementary solutions to build on your tax team’s strengths.
FeaturesCard.Description6: One single system that saves time, improves morale, and lets you take on higher-profile projects.
FeaturesCard.Description7: Easily configure new products or add new users to adjust the system to your business changes.
FeaturesCard.Description8: Automatically generate signature-ready sales and use tax returns for easy filing, or let IncorporateTax handle filing and remittance for you.
ImageSection.Title: Everything you need to slay with your taxes
ImageDection.Description: Adding maximum efficiency and empowering your business to reach full potencial by optimizing tax lifecycle.
ImageSection.Card.Description1: We take security seriously. Protecting your tax information while you're filling and when you're finished is our top priority, always.
ImageSection.Card.Description2: We update our software anytime the tax laws change, so your return is guaranteed and accurate for the year you're filling.
ImageSection.Card.Description3: Get the help you need when you need it with unlimited email and phone support. Need more? Get advices from an IncorporateTax expert.
Info.FirstSection.Title: We'll get your taxes done right
Info.FirstSection.Description: As taxes get more complex, tax teams need to master the technology, business processes and analytics in order to enhance their performance. Our team will get you there with the exact level of assistance you require.
Info.SecondSection.Title: Take advantage of time-saving features to start filing with confidence
Info.SecondtSection.Description: Get the right professional tax software package and pricing for your business. With our simple and user-friendly tool, data is easy to find, sort and report on. Maximize your productivity by including integrated add-on solutions to complete your online tax workflow.
